vernac_cmds: Lemma handleAppendEntries_currentTerm_monotonic: forall h st (d : raft_data) (m : msg) (t : term) (n : name) (pli : logIndex) (plt : term) (es : list entry) (ci : logIndex), handleAppendEntries h st t n pli plt es ci = (d, m) -> currentTerm st <= currentTerm d.
